NG","body":"是嗎？\n我從那時開始就一直被我老爸說我一臉凶神惡煞的了。\n你看，我旁邊騎在機車上的人，這就是我老爸","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event142-02-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"真，真的耶！\n我昨天才在Galaxy跟老闆打過招呼！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event142-02-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"然後對面的這個人是銀河拉麵的店長。\n後面的人是Death Galaxy的主唱","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event142-02-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"是各位前輩年輕時的照片……！\n雖然非常帥氣，但看起來卻意外地普通呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"kime01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event142-02-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"嗯？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event142-02-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"啊，不是！　因為樂團名叫「Death Galaxy」\n所以我想說團員們應該會化很厲害的妝……\n畢竟，都選用「Death」這個單字了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event142-02-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"什麼啊，這還用說嗎。\n下台後當然是普通的打扮啊","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event142-02-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"老爸有說過這張照片是\n有次Death Galaxy專場LIVE大成功的時候拍的","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event142-02-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"也不曉得老爸他們是因為怎樣\n但就是騎